description:
Poco F6 Pro HyperPower Evolved
Snapdragon® 8 Gen 2 120W HyperCharge
WQHD+ Flow AMOLED
50MP triple camera with OIS
Capture clearer images with the Light Fusion 800 image sensor
Smart 120W HyperCharge
Massive 5000mAh (typ) battery
WQHD+ 120Hz Flow AMOLED
4000 nits peak brightness for brilliant visuals
Premium design with metal frame
Smooth quad-curved glass back
WQHD+ Flow AMOLED display
POCO F6 Pro incorporates flagship-level light-emitting material with greater luminous efficiency and lower power consumption. It boasts an ultra-high peak brightness of 4000 nits* and a Pro HDR display which can achieve up to 8 times more brightness, you can enjoy even more stunning visuals with sharp contrast and vivid details.
Professional-level colour experience
POCO F6 Pro reproduces accurate and stunning colours using colour calibration based on CIE 2015 standards. Each display is finely tuned before leaving the factory, ensuring colour-matching based on human visual perception.
Wet Touch display
Easier to use
Wet touch display technology improves touch recognition when you're hands are wet, when it's raining, and in damp conditions.
In-screen fingerprint sensor
Supports heart rate monitoring*
Enjoy fast unlocking experience and less stimulus on eyes in low light conditions. You can also keep tabs on your heart rate with the in-screen fingerprint sensor.
